OL,3,CBlue cards and sin bins to be delayed
OL,4,Cafter talks with Fifa
OL,6,FThe International Football Association
OL,7,FBoard, who decide the rules of
OL,8,Ffootball, have proposed plans to trial
OL,9,F'blue cards' for sin bins in
OL,10,Fprofessional football
OL,12,FThe decision to announce when blue
OL,13,Fcards will be trialled in football has
OL,14,Fbeen kicked into March by the after
OL,15,Fbacklash from managers, players and
OL,16,Ffans.
OL,18,FInitially scheduled to be announced on
OL,19,FFriday, ITV News understands that
OL,20,Ftrial proposals have been delayed
OL,21,Ffollowing discussions with Fifa.
