OL,3,CBlue cards and sin bins to be delayed
OL,4,Cafter talks with Fifa
OL,6,FBlue cards had been set to be
OL,7,Fintroduced to football more than 50
OL,8,Fyears after the red and yellow cards
OL,9,Fwere first brought into the game.
OL,11,FPlayers would be shown a blue card if
OL,12,Fthey commit a cynical foul, or show
OL,13,Fdissent towards a referee, linesman or
OL,14,Ffourth official, the International
OL,15,FFootball Association Board (IFAB) has
OL,16,Fsaid.
