OL,3,CBlue cards and sin bins to be delayed
OL,4,Cafter talks with Fifa
OL,6,FThey would mark the biggest
OL,7,Fdisciplinary shake-up in the sport
OL,8,Fsince the 1970 Mexico World Cup where
OL,9,Fred and yellow cards were first
OL,10,Fintroduced.
OL,12,FBlue cards, along with sin-bin trials
OL,13,Fand other measures are hoped to
OL,14,Fimprove player behaviour.
OL,16,FPremier League managers and legends
OL,17,Fhave already blasted the decision,
OL,18,Fwith former Arsenal player and pundit
OL,19,FPaul Merson dubbing the blue cards a
OL,20,F"waste of time".
