OL,3,CBlue cards and sin bins to be delayed
OL,4,Cafter talks with Fifa
OL,6,FChief among those pushing back on the
OL,7,Fidea was Liverpool manager Jurgen
OL,8,FKlopp, who stated he couldn't remember
OL,9,F"the last time they (IFAB) had a
OL,10,Ffantastic idea if ever".
OL,12,FKlopp, who has recently announced that
OL,13,Fhe would be walking away from
OL,14,FLiverpool at the end of the season,
OL,15,Fsaid: "The introduction of a new card
OL,16,Fwill give more opportunities to fail
OL,17,Fas well, and the discussion will be
OL,18,Fabout should it be a blue card, should
OL,19,Fit be a yellow card, in the good old
OL,20,Ftimes it would have been a red card or
OL,21,Fa yellow.
