OL,6,F"These things make it more difficult,
OL,7,Fif they want to test it then I have no
OL,8,Fproblem with testing, but if that is a
OL,9,Ffirst step to agreeing or it happening.
OL,11,F'The game and the image of the game is
OL,12,Fbeing tarnished by the behaviour of
OL,13,Fplayers,' said former head of Premier
OL,14,FLeague referees Keith Hackett
OL,16,F"I don't know it doesn't sound like a
OL,17,Ffantastic idea in the first moment,
OL,18,Fbut I don't know when the last time
OL,19,Fthey had a fantastic idea these guys
OL,20,Fif they ever did, I am 56, never."
