OL,3,CBlue cards and sin bins to be delayed
OL,4,Cafter talks with Fifa
OL,6,FTottenham boss Ange Postecoglou,
OL,7,FEverton's Sean Dyche and Crystal
OL,8,FPalace's Roy Hodgson are among those
OL,9,Fwho have voiced criticism for the new
OL,10,Frules.
OL,12,FWhat is happening?
OL,14,FThe IFAB, the governing body that
OL,15,Fdetermines the laws of the game of
OL,16,Fassociation football, was set to
OL,17,Fpublish protocols on Friday in an
OL,18,Feffort to improve participant
OL,19,Fbehaviour, including trials for a sin-
OL,20,Fbin.
