OL,3,CBlue cards and sin bins to be delayed
OL,4,Cafter talks with Fifa
OL,6,FSin-bins have been trialled
OL,7,Fsuccessfully at grassroots level and
OL,8,Fare now set to be tested
OL,10,FHowever, during the initial trial
OL,11,Fphase, top-level competitions will not
OL,12,Fbe involved. This is to avoid
OL,13,Fconfusion among players ` for instance
OL,14,Fif their domestic league ran a trial
OL,15,Fbut a continental competition they
OL,16,Fwere involved in at the same time did
OL,17,Fnot.
OL,19,FIt is not precisely clear what level
OL,20,Fthe new protocols will be stress-
OL,21,Ftested at initially.
