OL,6,FWhat's this about blue cards?
OL,8,FIt is understood referees will use
OL,9,Fblue cards to indicate a player must
OL,10,Fgo to the sin-bin.
OL,12,FSin-bins will be used for two specific
OL,13,Foffences ` dissent and tactical fouls,
OL,14,Fsuch as Giorgio Chiellini's tug on
OL,15,FBukayo Saka in the Euro 2020 final.
