OL,3,CBlue cards and sin bins to be delayed
OL,4,Cafter talks with Fifa
OL,6,FPlayers will be ordered to go to the
OL,7,Ftechnical area for ten minutes. If a
OL,8,Fplayer has already been booked, a blue
OL,9,Fcard will mean they are sent off. Two
OL,10,Fblue cards will also result in
OL,11,Fdismissal.
OL,13,FWhat other measures are the IFAB
OL,14,Flooking at?
OL,16,FAs well as sin-bins, competitions will
OL,17,Fhave the option to trial 'captain only
OL,18,Fzones'.
